<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-101-468  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 101 468.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Macworld  Feb 1990 v7 n2 p191(2).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Language Master personal computer dictionary and thesaurus;MacProof 3.2.1. (Software Review) (Franklin Software's LanguageMaster, Lexpertise Linguistic Software's MacProof 3.2.1 stylechecker desk accessory) (evaluation)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Lukos, Gerry.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>Franklin Software's $99 Language Master dictionary and thesaurusdesk accessory and Lexpertise Linguistic Software's $195 MacProof3.2.1 style checker desk accessory are add-on programs thatprovide enhancements for a variety of word processing programs.andO;Language Master contains a 80,000 word dictionary and 40,000 wordthesaurus; this mass of information is used in a number of ways.andO;Definitions can be presented for each word, inflections ordifferent forms of the word listed, correct hyphenation shown, andsynonyms provided.andP;  MacProof was found to be a much betterwriter's tool than Language Master and it can be customized toaddress the weaknesses of the individual writer.andP;  MacProof canhelp detect problems concerning style and usage, and it includes aspell checker.andP;  The program is able to examine a documentobjectively, even when the user no longer can.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   Franklin Software Inc. (products)Lexpertise USA Inc. (products).andO;Product:   Language Master (Computer program)MacProof 3.2.1 (Computer program).andO;Topic:     EvaluationUtility ProgramsAdd-In-On SoftwareSoftware packages.andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>